title: Colin Cowherd Podcast - Colin’s Week 1 NFL Reaction
itunes:title: Colin Cowherd Podcast - Colin’s Week 1 NFL Reaction
description:
Colin reacts to the afternoon slate of NFL games, including the Vikings stomping of the Packers, Mitch Trubisky’s dub over Joe Burrow, and Bill Belichick's apparent New England decline.
